\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
begin{example}
\backslash
label{example}
\end_layout

\end_inset

 Let 
\begin_inset Formula $V$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $W$
\end_inset

 be finite-dimensional 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{C}$
\end_inset

-vector spaces and let 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

 be an open subspace of 
\begin_inset Formula $V$
\end_inset

.
 For each open subset 
\begin_inset Formula $U$
\end_inset

 of 
\begin_inset Formula $X$
\end_inset

, we define 
\begin_inset Formula 
